#

Masoor Dal with Spinach and Brown Rice

$12.5
350 kcal

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh-ProteinGluten-Free

Tags:

IndianDinnerVegetarianHigh-Protein

Description

A protein-packed Indian lentil dish with spinach, served with nutty brown rice.

Ingredients

  • Masoor dal (red lentils): 1 cup
  • Fresh spinach: 2 cups
  • Brown rice: 1 cup
  • Onion: 1, chopped
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Ginger: 1 inch, grated
  • Cumin seeds: 1 teaspoon
  • Turmeric powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Garam masala: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Vegetable oil or ghee: 2 tablespoons
  • Fresh cilantro: for garnish
